profile:
At Hometurf Lawn Care, we have been treating the lawns of our loyal customers for over 30 years. As a family-owned and -operated business, we have grown by delivering lush, healthy, green lawns while using only the highest quality products applied by professional lawn care technicians. Let us help you make your lawn look its best this season!

Our season-long lawn care programs take the guess work out of which products to use and when. Applications are scheduled to be applied four to six weeks apart throughout the season for optimal turf care. We strive to ensure everything your lawn needs is included in our programs. No telemarketing or sales calls pushing unnecessary extras.

Our services include: lawn care programs, lawn maintenance programs, fertilizer, weed control, insect control, aeration, grass seeding, dethatching, top dressing, chinch bug control and grub control.

profile:
Assiniboine Lights & Landscapes has been operating in Calgary for over 15 years. Our services include landscape construction, property maintenance, snow removal and professional Christmas light installations. At Assiniboine we work very hard to ensure that our customers are happy and that we are providing a first rate service.
   
Assiniboine's Landscape Construction Division: specializes in stone patios & pathways, retaining walls, decks & railings, fences & gates, pergolas, flower beds, sodding, grading, planting and so much more. No matter the size of your project, Assiniboine is equipped to do the job.
   
Assiniboine's Property Maintenance Division: services residential, condominium and commercial properties. Our services include weekly and bi-weekly lawn care, vacation cuts, hedge and tree pruning, bed maintenance and fertilization. We also offer Spring and Fall clean up packages to start and end the season right.
   
Assiniboine's Snow Removal & Ice Management Division: services both residential, condominium, and commercial properties. Our crews use everything from shovels, scrapers and snow blowers to skid steers, power brushes, snow plows, sanders and dump trucks to ensure the safety of our clients.
  
Assiniboine's Christmas Light Division: provides the best installations in the business. We specialize in large trees, steep roofs and bringing attention to your home or business during the holiday season. We take great pride in providing a professional, hassle-free service during a busy time of year for everyone.

I take much pride to introduce to you Alberta's 'If We Didn't Build It Wasn't Built Rite' fencing company.  Built Rite Fence Inc. is a second generation family fencing company and was established in 2001 by Desi Specht.  Desi worked for his father's fencing company in Northern Ontario from the time he was 15 and is carrying on his family legacy with Built Rite Fence Inc.
Built Rite Fence Inc is a professional fencing company supplying and installing residential, commercial and industrial styles of fencing throughout Alberta. 
We specialize in: 
Chain Link Fencing, and Gates 
Post and Cable
Sports Courts

Plated Cages 
Baseball Backstops 
Bollards Posts
Signs (stop signs, yield signs)
Turn-Key Security Fences & Gates 
Automated Gate Systems
Cantilever Gates 
Wood Fences 
Snow Fences (Commercial Only)
Fence Repairs 
Garbage Encloses 
Hauling: Enclosed trailers, flat decks, dump trailers & Dump Trucks
